rows.label: tev055601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Hoy! Friend wants information? Hmm...
Information of Cheche veeery expensive.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0002
rows.name:
But since Cheche going to be staying in city of friend
for while, only fair that Cheche make special exception
this one time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0003
rows.name:
Nopon very wise race that live in caravans around
Mira. Nopon travel from caravans to every corner of
planet selling fabulous wares![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0004
rows.name:
Business sort of hurting these days because of so many
unexpected visitors...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0005
rows.name:
But gullib...uh, reliable friends like humans fill all
Nopon with newfound hope![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0010
rows.name:
Cheche come here just as soon as Cheche catch wind
of big new town.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0011
rows.name:
It turns out that human food is delicious!
Plus there are tons of ways to make easy money.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0012
rows.name:
Everyone else in caravans should get Nopon heinies
over here lickety-split![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0013
rows.name:
Then Cheche can sell Nopon inside info about city and
REALLY rake it in![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0018
rows.name:
Does friend know human named Vandham?
Really big guy?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0019
rows.name:
According to sources of Cheche, this Vandham fellow
wants to sign friendship treaty with Nopon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0020
rows.name:
So why the holdup?! Friend is BLADE, right?
Friend should convince Vandham to get ball rolling so
Nopon are officially allowed to live here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG0021
rows.name:
Then Cheche can sell Nopon inside info about city and
REALLY rake it in![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1001
rows.name:
Meh! Human friend very smart. Knows exactly which
Nopon to go to for answers![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1002
rows.name:
Cheche knows all about your FrontierNav.
It is big wonder machine for gathering information
about Mira, right?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1003
rows.name:
...Wrong! Compared to extensive mental database
of Cheche, FrontierNav is only oversized toy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1004
rows.name:
But lucky for friend, Cheche willing to part with juiciest
secrets of Mira for low, low price of 1,000,000,000
credits. Such deals![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1005
rows.name:
...Meh? Friend cannot pay this entirely reasonable sum?
Such shame! Cheche ready to throw in meaning of life
for free, too...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1010
rows.name:
Thanks to new friendship treaty, Nopon friends of
Cheche already pouring into city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1011
rows.name:
Cheche able to point them at best restaurants for
modest price. Also provide business advice for very
reasonable commission.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1012
rows.name:
New Nopon so very eager to make Cheche filthy
stinking rich![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1013
rows.name:
Meh-meh! Cheche just LOVE new human friends!
Friendship treaties like gifts that keep giving![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1014
rows.name:
Cheche better hurry up and find more info to sell
so cash flow stays healthy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1019
rows.name:
Friend knows strange human person named Eliza?
She gives many speeches in residential district.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1020
rows.name:
Mostly she talks about "equality" and "freedom."
Like those can be sold. Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1021
rows.name:
But she still seems nice. Very trusting! Cheche thinking
she might buy information for triple usual price.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG1022
rows.name:
First Cheche need to find suave approach.
Suave approach key to making huge coin![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2001
rows.name:
Cheche mobilizing best informants in Cauldros to get
best scoops about continent.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2002
rows.name:
All Cheche need is one mind-blowing piece of intel to
take business to new level![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2003
rows.name:
What BLADE heading to certain doom in Ganglion
stronghold would NOT pay 10,000,000,000,000 credits
for shot at staying alive?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2004
rows.name:
No BLADE, says Cheche! Come back soon and friend
can be first victi...uh, customer. Yes. Customer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2010
rows.name:
Wise Cheche really gets around.
Visited many, many places on Mira.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2011
rows.name:
But Cheche never seen someone as willing to put
others before self as Eliza.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2012
rows.name:
Just other day, Cheche got picked on by young and
disagreeable human ruffianâ€”but Eliza came to rescue
like Cheche her own family![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2013
rows.name: Maybe Cheche not charge Eliza for info anymore.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2014
rows.name:
...What? Cheche very GENEROUS? Meh-meh-meh!
Friend is sorely mistaken! Now Cheche got to charge
other friends more to make up for lost business.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2020
rows.name:
Nopon friends in Cauldros sending all kinds of useful
info back to Cheche.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2021
rows.name:
Market value must be 10,000,000,000,000 credits
at least. Only one problem...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2022
rows.name:
Eliza worry about BLADEs going into battle there,
so she give away best info for free.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2023
rows.name:
So here it is! First juicy info: Slavebird Isle off coast
of Cauldros has incredibly delicious food called
brambloo shoot![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2024
rows.name:
Second juicy info: Really bad idea to touch bullet flies
buzzing around cliffs above the Scholes Battlegrounds.
Friend will get hurt. Possibly dead.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev055601_MSG2025
rows.name:
...See? No longer profitable, but very useful intel.
BLADE friends are lucky Cheche has such astoundingly
reliable connections.[ST:wait ]
